properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from  Suwannee River to Keaton Beach out 20 NM; Apalachee Bay or Coastal Waters From Keaton Beach to Ochlockonee River Fl out to 20 Nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 19 at 3:27AM EST until January 20 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds around 20 knots with gusts up to 25 knots
expected.

* WHERE...Nearshore Gulf waters from the Ochlockonee River to
the Suwannee River out 20 nautical miles.

* WHEN...From 7 PM this evening to 1 PM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 PM THIS EVENING TO 1 PM EST MONDAY
